docs.abstract: Ukrainian opposition unit that took control of Pres Viktor F Yanukovych's sprawling residential compound posts guards around it and prevents looting, even as swarms of gawking Kiev residents stroll through its grounds; street fighters say that they want to preserve evidence of the ousted leader's lavish lifestyle for his prosecution.
